The most precious memory in her neural cloud is this teatime spent with you.
A heartfelt return gift from your Doll, obtained after forming a Covenant.

Have you received the sweetheart's signal from this cute little broker?
A heartfelt return gift from your Doll, obtained after forming a Covenant.

A heartfelt return gift from your Doll, obtained after forming a Covenant.

Justice was always her sole credo. But now, your ideals have also become a fundamental motivation for her.

data.introduction:
Unnamed hero in the shadows, your deeds and achievements shall be immortalized in big data.

data.introduction:
Remain calm and collected, gather trustworthy companions, and a previously impossible escape becomes possible.
Unlocked by completing all Escape from Cyborg story stages.

Belka has no ability to enter dreams, but she can still steal away the Commander's heart.
Unlocked by acquiring Belka's Outfit - Enchanting Imp

data.introduction:
The surprise has been prepared, and the long-awaited anniversary will arrive soon!

data.introduction:
Filled with joy, the squirrel finally conveys her feelings.

data.introduction:
She gracefully removes her gloves, awaiting you to take her hands and spin with her in the hall's center.

data.introduction:
Do not be deceived by her messy, laid-back appearance, look into her eyes. Those belong to that of a born huntress.
Unlocked after obtaining Peritya's outfit - Born Huntress

data.introduction:
Okay, alright! Relax! You just need to reboot.
Unlocked by claiming the final reward from Into the Shadows - Assessment Prep

data.introduction:
After much wandering, Andoris finally found the place that suited her best.
Unlocked by completing all story stages for Into the Shadows

data.introduction:
Cats are the treasures of the world, no matter what era it is.

data.introduction:

"Cheating is not allowed, okay?"
Unlocked by completing Mímisbrunnr's Loop - Part I

Even if I am imprisoned here forever, my neural cloud remains unshakable. As long as the good in my life remains, I will not abandon hope.

data.name: Portrait - Athletics Rookie
data.introduction:
She extends you an invitation to exercise with an avoidant gaze, apprehensively awaiting your nod of affirmation.
Unlocked after obtaining Lotta's outfit - Athletics Rookie

data.name: Portrait - Flying Phantom
data.introduction:
The light is destined to be followed by shadows. This is her choice, and her acceptance of the light. 
Unlocked after obtaining Lenna's outfit - Flying Phantom

data.introduction:
The clear pool water traces her dazzling curves. The show's about to begin; come take your seat, Commander.
Unlocked after obtaining Sharkry's outfit - Swimsuit Idol.

data.introduction:
"I'm sorry. Thank you. Goodbye. I'm home." This is the declaration of her return, and the promise she made with you.
Unlocked after obtaining Colphne's outfit - Silent Heart.

data.name: Portrait - Manifold Revelry
data.introduction:
Laugh and rejoice until the curtain falls on the festivities.

The heat of the stove and its fragrant steam give people courage and motivation.

Colors might fade, but good memories will remain vibrant forever.

Now that this perfect dance has finally hit the stage, has Yoohee succeeded in conveying her true feelings?
Unlocked by clearing all stages of Snowclad Whisper in normal mode

data.introduction:
She uses her concerts to bring joy and happiness to everyone, allowing them to cast off their worries and cares and enjoy every wonderful moment of their lives.
Unlock by obtaining Yoohee's Outfit - Miracle Sweetheart.

data.name: Portrait - Flurry Crimson
data.introduction:
Like an unstoppable searing storm, she sweeps aways all the thorns in her path, her glory existing for you alone.
Unlocked after obtaining Faye's Outfit - Flurry Crimson.

data.name: Icon - Shadow Agent
data.introduction:
Training is just the start. The true clash of life and death is only just beginning.

data.name: Icon - Lightbearer
data.introduction:
Though she is alone in the dark, her heart still harbors the light of hope. 
Unlocks after completing the Ex Umbra Story Mode stages.

data.name: Portrait Frame - Buried Feelings

Even when reduced to cold data, she won't forget to love you.
Unlocked by completing all Challenge Mode stages for Snowclad Whisper.

data.name: Portrait Frame - Balefire Shift
data.introduction:
Unpredictable tactics that turn the tide— A special award from B.R.I.E.F.
Unlocked after ranking in the top 50% in the Military Simulation: Balefire Shift.

data.name: Icon Frame - Altius Descendat

Only through darkness can there be light
Unlocked by completing all Challenge Mode stages for Ex Umbra.

data.name: Icon Frame - The Cultured Commander
data.introduction:
Isn't displaying your precious memories a form of art?
Unlocked after Overall Recollection Score reaches 1200.

data.name: Icon Frame - Great Collector
data.introduction:
The Curio Display shall shine once again!
Unlocked after Overall Recollection Score reaches 2450.

data.name: Icon Frame - Unstoppable Advance
data.introduction:
The combination of inter-team collaborating and individualism wins absolute glory on the emerald pitch.
Obtained as the theme prize of completing the Coordination Drill "Divegrass Drill".

data.name: Outfit - Summer Pitcher
data.introduction:
Nagant's outfit box contains a baseball. The ball held by the plush duck must feel even better. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Summer Pitcher in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Krolik's Combat Suit - Training Outfit
data.introduction:
The outfit box containing Krolik's Combat Suit. You can see that it contains the training uniforms uniformly issued to the Elmo. The design is simple and clean, with strong functionality. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Krolik's Training Outfit in the dress-up interface.
data.description: 克罗丽科的标准战斗装备

data.name: Nemesis' Combat Suit - Training Outfit
data.introduction:
The outfit box containing Nemesis' Combat Suit. Inside is the training outfit uniformly distributed to Elmo. The design is simple and clean, and it is very functional. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Nemesis' Training Outfit in the dress-up interface.
data.description: 纳美西丝的标准战斗装备

data.name: Colphne's Combat Suit - Training Outfit
data.introduction:
The outfit box containing Colphne's Combat Suit. You can see that it includes the training outfits issued to Elmo. The design is simple and clean, with solid functionality. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Colphne's Training Outfit in the dress-up interface.
data.description: 寇尔芙的标准战斗装备

data.name: Groza's Combat Suit - Training Outfit
data.introduction:
The outfit box containing Groza's Combat Suit. Inside is the uniform for training that was uniformly distributed to Elmo. The design is simple and clean, and it is very functional. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Groza's Training Outfit in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Prancing Bunny
data.introduction:
Krolik's outfit box. The box is very light, and inside is probably a set of light outfits as its selling point. You can envision Krolik's agile figure running fast on the battlefield after wearing it. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Bouncing Bunny in the dress-up interface.
data.description: 克罗丽科累充活动皮肤

data.name: Combat Suit - Dawn of Battle
data.introduction:
The outfit box containing Groza's Combat Suit. The box contains heavy dark arm armor. Wearing it, Groza will surely be in for a tough fight. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Dawn of Battle in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Serene Dark River
data.introduction:
Nemesis' Outfit Box. Inside is a black and purple outfit full of mystery. Nemesis' wardrobe cannot be without it. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Serene Dark River in the dress-up interface.
data.description: 衣装·纳美西丝的商城衣装

data.name: Combat Suit - Wandering Star Trail
data.introduction:
The outfit box containing Nemesis' Combat Suit. The box includes a uniquely styled head ornament. What thoughts went through Nemesis' neural mind when she wore this outfit? 
After obtaining it, you can unlock the Wandering Star Trail in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Combat Suit - Sparkling Wish
data.introduction:
The outfit box containing Vepley's Combat Suit. Inside the box is a set of warm-looking clothes. Wearing it, Vepley will surely bring the light of hope and happiness to every viewer. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock the Sparkling Wish in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Sangria Succulent
data.introduction:
Groza's outfit box. Inside is a gorgeous and memorable outfit. Whether in the past or now, Groza, wearing it, will always stand by the Commander's side. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Violet Drizzle in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Narcissus
data.introduction: Daiyan's Outfit box. Inside is an elegant and memorable dress. The time spent with the Commander must be unforgettable for Daiyan. After obtaining it, you can unlock Exquisite Jade in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Combat Suit - Vitality Magic
data.introduction:
The outfit box containing Lenna's Combat Suit. Inside is a unique Outfit. Cheer up! It's magic from Lenna♪ 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Vitality Magic in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Summer Echoes
data.introduction: This is Vepley's outfit box. Inside, there's a blue and white performance outfit. Upon receiving it, Vepley must be filled with anticipation for a summer performance, right? After obtaining it, you can unlock "Summer Echo" in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Ballroom Interlude
data.introduction:
Makiatto's outfit box. Inside is a simple and elegant dress. Although the ball has ended, Makiatto still awaits the Commander's next invitation. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock the Dancing Pausing in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Celestial River at Dusk
data.introduction:
Tololo's Outfit Box. Inside, you can see a swimsuit with a light-colored cover-up. The simple color scheme and romantic style perfectly complement Tololo. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Celestial River at Dusk in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Sparkling Ocean
data.introduction:
This is Suomi's outfit box. Inside, there's a playful swimsuit. She even adjusted her hairstyle specifically so the ribbons of her outfit could flow freely. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock the Sparkling Ocean in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Strawberry Zabaione
data.introduction:
Sabrina's Outfit Box. Even unopened, a sweet and refreshing aroma drifts out.
After obtaining it, you can unlock the Strawberry Zabaione in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Superspeed Chequer
data.introduction:
Zhaohui's outfit box. Inside contains a light and breezy summer racing-themed outfit set. Zhaohui is very pleased with the clean and sharp design.
This can be used to obtain the outfit "Superspeed Chequer" in the dressing interface.

data.name: Outfit - Speed Star
data.introduction:
Klukai's Outfit Box. The box contains a silver-white rider's outfit. This customized clothing is perfectly tailored to fit Klukai's frame and is essential gear for a knight's debut.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Speed Star in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Sparks on the Circuit
data.introduction:
Cheeta's Outfit Box. Inside is a snug-fitting outfit radiating a sense of speed. The roar of engines and Cheeta's smug laughter seem to echo in your ears when you see it. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Sparks on the Circuit in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Enchanting Imp
data.introduction:
Belka's Outfit Box. The box contains a close-fitting outfit that seems to be for use during Halloween. With such a tantalizing posture, one has to wonder whose dreams this imp aims to invade.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Enchanting Imp in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Astral Luminous
data.introduction:
Klukai's Outfit Box. The box contains a slim-fitting rider's outfit and a black tactical vest. A dashing figure flashes past the battlefield, leaving only the sound of roaring engines behind.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Astral Luminous in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Queen in Radiance
data.introduction:
Springfield's Outfit Box. The box contains a gorgeous violet-colored formal dress. The elegant design hides traces of an invasive boldness and cunning.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Queen in Radiance in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Born Huntress
data.introduction:
Peritya's Outfit Box. The box contains a set of flamboyantly colored sportswear. One can unleash more of their hunter's instinct if one is willing to travel light.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Born Huntress in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Embroidered Bamboo, Blooming Shadows
data.introduction:
Makiatto's Outfit Box, containing an embroidered dress that's perfect for early spring. Its material is lustrous and smooth, and it has a faint fragrance to it. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Embroidered Bamboo, Blooming Shadows in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Athletics Rookie
data.introduction:
Lotta's outfit box contains a set of lightweight and breathable sportswear. As an entry-grade product, it combines versatility and value for money, making it very suitable for rookie athletes.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Competitive Rookie in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Night Huntress
data.introduction:
Lenna's outfit box contains a wingsuit for clandestine operations. Not only does it facilitate covert operations at night, it's also light and wards off the cold.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Flying Phantom in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Swimsuit Idol
data.introduction:
Sharkry's Outfit Box. It contains a custom-fitted competition swimsuit. Even off the stage, Sharkry is still the center of attention!
After obtaining it, you can unlock Swimsuit Idol in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Silent Heart
data.introduction:
Colphne's Outfit Box. It contains a neatly-folded set of nursing Doll attire. Surely changing back into this uniform is a sign that Colphne's ready to take on her new destiny.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Silent Heart in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Crimson Gale
data.introduction:
Faye's outfit box. Contains a lightweight combat outfit for easy movement. Made with lightweight and durable materials, it is both aesthetic and protective.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Flurry Crimson in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Miracle Sweetheart
data.introduction:
Yoohee's outfit box. Contains a cute maid's uniform. Its sheer, satiny elegance accentuates the wearer's charms and it smells faintly of candy.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Miracle Sweetheart in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Dance Like The Blazing Sun
data.introduction:
Nikketa's outfit box. Inside is a cheerleader uniform that she made herself. 
Its lively design radiates the vigor of youth. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Dance Like The Blazing Sun in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Molotov Bunny
data.introduction:
Vector's outfit box. Inside is a covert battle dress uniform made of composite materials. Its stretchable fabric combines mobility and comfort. 
After obtaining it, you can unlock Molotov Bunny in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Outfit - Vivi Sometimes Hides Her Molotovs
data.introduction:
Vector's outfit box, containing school uniform-themed clothing.。
The jacket uses muted colors and is paired with a dark blue skirt, combining an air of academic authority while preserving the schoolgirl spirit.
After obtaining it, you can unlock Vivi Sometimes Hides Her Molotovs in the dress-up interface.

data.name: Electronic Edge
data.introduction: A replaceable blade attachment. When activated, the blade is wrapped in a lethal high-density energy field. This grants it the capability to efficiently cut through flesh, bone, and most types of armor.

data.name: Rifle Suppressor
data.introduction: Universal flash suppressor for assault rifles, submachine guns, and rapid-fire machine guns. Effectively prevents barrel flash for self-concealment.
data.description: 配件-紫精通普通 新手引导特作

data.name: Breahing Point
data.introduction: Gain Scoring Points*100

data.name: Compile Point
data.introduction: Gain Compile Points*100

data.name: Universal Unit
data.introduction: A device that can open electronic security gates using unique encryption technology. Due to its delicate manufacturing, it needs to be stored with care. The carrier often needs to ensure smooth movement, which affects their movement speed and shooting accuracy.

data.name: Compile Point
data.introduction: Gain Compile Points*50

data.name: Electro Crystals
data.introduction:
Irregular crystals with a metallic luster. It has some degree of Collapse radiation, so it is best not to hold on to them for too long.
Can be used to unlock nodes in Strategies.
data.description: 用于暗区天赋的升级道具

data.name: Delve Permit
data.introduction:
Even the best kind of support has limits. Be careful not to go too deep into the hinterland.
Used up by entering areas. Refreshed once you return from Exploration.

data.name: Gravel
data.introduction: A bottle of standard gravel, with sparkling collapse crystal particles. It can be exchanged for pickup points at the host and is especially popular with Baruch.

data.name: Elite Doll Neural Custom Gift Box
data.introduction: The custom gift box contains Neural Archives of Elite Dolls, specially prepared by the surrogate. Upon opening, you can choose and obtain 1 Elite Doll's Neural Archive. Available options include: Vepley, Peritya, Sabrina, Tololo, and Qiongjiu.

data.name: Standard Doll Neural Custom Gift Box
data.introduction: The custom gift box contains Neural Archives of Standard Dolls, specially prepared by the surrogate. Upon opening, you can choose and obtain 1 Standard Doll's Neural Archive. Available options include: Groza, Krolik, Nemesis, Colphne, Sharkry, Cheeta, Nagant, Ksenia, and Littara.

data.name: Elite Weapon Neural Custom Gift Box
data.introduction: The custom gift box contains Elite Weapons, specially prepared by the surrogate. Upon opening, you can choose and obtain 1 Elite Weapon. Available options include: Heart Seeker, Optical Illusion, Planeta, Golden Melody, Samosek, and Mezzaluna.

data.name: Standard Weapon Neural Custom Gift Box
data.introduction: The custom gift box contains Standard Weapons, specially prepared by the surrogate. Upon opening, you can choose and obtain 1 Standard Weapon. Available options include: OTs-14, .380 Curva, .50 Nemesis, Hare, Vepr-12, Pecheneg-SP, Robinson Modular Rifle, MP7H1, Model Alpha, QBZ-191, Sportivo Calibro 12, Nagant M1895, Three-line Rifle M1891, Stechkin, and Model ARM.

data.name: Elite Neural Pre-storage Gift Box [Discarded]
data.introduction: The gift box containing random Elite Doll Neural Archives, a surprise specially prepared by the surrogate. After opening it, you can get the Neural archive of a random Elite Doll. Available options include: Vepley, Peritya, Sabrina, Tololo, and Qiongjiu.

data.name: Standard Neural Gift Box [Abandoned]
data.introduction: The gift box containing random Standard Doll Neural Archives, a surprise specially prepared by the surrogate. After opening it, you can get the Neural archive of a random Standard Doll. Available options include: Groza, Krolik, Nemesis, Colphne, Sharkry, and Cheeta.

data.name: Elite Weapon Pre-Storage Gift Box [Discarded]
data.introduction: The custom gift box contains random Elite Weapons, a surprise specially prepared by the surrogate. Upon opening, you can choose and obtain 1 Elite Weapon. Available options include: Heart Seeker, Optical Illusion, Planeta, Golden Melody, and Mezzaluna.

data.name: Standard Weapon Pre-Storage Gift Box [Discarded]
data.introduction: The custom gift box contains Standard Weapons, a surprise specially prepared by the surrogate. Upon opening, you can choose and obtain 1 Standard Weapon. Available options include: OTs-14, .380 Curva, .50 Nemesis, Hare, Vepr-12, Pecheneg-SP, Robinson Modular Rifle, MP7H1, Model Alpha, QBZ-191, and Sportivo Calibro 12.

data.name: Monthly Crystal Contract
data.introduction: A stable contract, suitable for bounty hunters looking for short-term profits. The contract takes effect from the date of purchase and is valid for 1 month. During the validity period, 80 Collapse Pieces can be obtained daily.

data.name: Monthly Incremental Contract
data.introduction:
A contract for sale, categorized as a network service. After use, the simulation data can be modified through some technical means. Bounty hunters who wish to improve their material acquisition efficiency can consider purchasing it.
The contract takes effect from the date of purchase and is valid for one month. During this time the yield for the first two runs of Standardizing Sync per day and the number of rewinds per day will be increased.

data.name: Hunter's Path Certification
data.introduction: A hardware device that stores digital certifications for specific routes. Hunter's Path routes can be loaded into Elmo's navigation system using this device. After use, the current Hunter's Path can be unlocked in the Voyage Journalism.

data.name: Broker's Path Certification
data.introduction: A hardware device that stores the digital certification of a specific route. The Broker's Path can be loaded into Elmo's navigation system using this device. After use, the current Broker's Path can be unlocked in the Voyage Journalism.

data.name: Re-Evaluation
data.introduction: A hardware device that stores route re-planning authorization, which can be used to re-plan the Hunter's Path and load the re-planned route into Elmo's Navigation system. After use, the unlocked current Hunter's Path can be upgraded to the current Broker's Path in the Voyage Journalism.

data.name: Reset Certificate
data.introduction: Reset Certificate - Reset BP

data.name: Surplus Goods Crate
Surplus Goods Crate
Journey Guardian Custom Gift Box
data.introduction: "The contamination zones are hazardous, so be prepared!" After opening it, you can choose and obtain 1 elite weapon. The optional weapons include [Classified Manuscript, Papa-Figo, Arcana, Guerno, Crowned Jackalope, Mjölnir, Expeditionary Pigeon].

data.name: Perfect Hunter Skin Crate
data.introduction:
An honorary gift from B.R.I.E.F., filled with various weapon skins to celebrate the birth of a new rookie in the contamination zone.
You can unlock the Phantom Game series of skins for 7 weapons upon opening.

data.name: Daily Free Gift Pack
data.introduction: Receive a free daily gift pack just by logging in. This pack may contain various rewards such as Access Permissions and Collapse Pieces. Login for a total of 21 days to guarantee an Access Permission ×1; 42 days to obtain a Basic Info Core ×1. This will reset after reaching this threshold.

data.name: Returnee Supply Gift Box
data.introduction:
To provide you, who returned to the Elmo, with timely and cost-effective supplies, to help you to rise to the top once again!
You can choose an item to receive upon opening the box.

data.name: Thanksgiving Neural Archive Custom Gift Box
data.introduction:
A Custom Gift Box containing Neural Archives of Targeted Dolls. An excellent choice for upgrading a Doll's combat capabilities. 
You can choose to receive one Neural Archive of a targeted Doll upon opening this Box. You can choose Dolls from the following list: Daiyan, Centaureissi, Lenna, Jiangyu, Makiatto, Ullrid, Suomi, Dushevnaya, Zhaohui, Klukai.
data.description: 周年庆自选限定人形宝箱

data.name: Thanksgiving Weapon Custom Gift Box
data.introduction:
A Custom Gift Box containing the exclusive weapons of Targeted Dolls. An excellent choice in upgrading combat capabilities.
You can choose to receive one targeted weapon upon opening this Box. You can choose weapons from the following list: Heavy Strings, Maid's Rules, Löwenjunges, Leaping Tiger, Bittersweet Caramel, Rectrix, Unspoken Calling, Eulogistic Verse, Juggernaut, Skylla.
data.description: 周年庆自选限定武器宝箱

data.name: Comrade Archive Custom Gift Box
data.introduction:
A Custom Gift Box containing Neural Archives of Standard Dolls. An excellent choice for upgrading a Doll's combat capabilities.
You can choose to receive one Neural Archive of a Standard Doll upon opening this Box. You can choose Dolls from the following list: Tololo, Qiongjiu, Vepley, Sabrina, Peritya, Mosin-Nagant.
data.description: 周年庆自选常驻人形宝箱

data.name: Companion Weapon Self-Select Pack
data.introduction:
A Custom Gift Box containing the exclusive weapons of Standard Dolls. An excellent choice in upgrading combat capabilities.
You can choose to receive one standard weapon upon opening this Box. You can choose weapons from the following list: Planeta, Golden Melody, Heart Seeker, Mezzaluna, Optical Illusion, Samosek.
data.description: 周年庆自选常驻武器宝箱

data.name: Weekly Supply Crate
data.introduction: Issued every week, with a chance to obtain a random reward for free. Possible rewards include Access Permissions, Collapse Pieces and so on. Opening a total of 3 boxes guarantees Targeted Access Permission x1, and opening a total of 6 boxes guarantees Collapse Pieces x300. The count is reset thereafter.

data.name: Frosted Glass
data.introduction: One of the sources of environmental information in the B.R.I.E.F. contaminated area. Artificial glass fragments that have been affected by Collapse radiation for a long time have transformed into glass-like crystals. The scraping of the Collapse storm has given it different shapes and colors. It can make carrier cards in analysis machines and is one of the most basic raw materials. It will be recycled after the current Boundary Chronicle project is completed.

data.name: Carbon Black Glass
data.introduction: One of the sources of environmental information in the B.R.I.E.F. contaminated area. After being affected by Collapse radiation for a long time, artificial glass mixed with a large amount of impurities reacts with each other to form glass-like crystals. Losing the transparency of glass, the chaotic gray-black color makes this type of crystal look more like metal or mineral. It can make carrier cards in analysis machines and is one of the most basic raw materials. It will be recycled after the current Boundary Chronicle project is completed.

data.name: Solid-State Glass
data.introduction: One of the sources of environmental information about the B.R.I.E.F. contaminated area is glass fragments scraped by the Collapse Storm, which re-forms into glass-like crystals after the solid-phase reaction caused by the long-term impact of the Collapse Radiation. They often appear in the gaps where debris quickly accumulates, and the shape is irregular. They are one of the most basic raw materials and can be used to make carrier cards in analytical machines. After the current Boundary Chronicle project is completed, they will be recycled.

data.name: Mixed Quartz
data.introduction: A mineral with high hardness belongs to quartzite, but due to high impurity content, it has lost the inherent commercial value of quartz. It can be combined with glass-like crystals in the analysis machine to make directional carrier cards. It will be recycled after the current Border Chronicle Project is completed.

data.name: Steel Shingle
data.introduction: Craft material fragments were widely used as a building material in the early years. It can be combined with glass-like crystals in the analysis machine to craft directional carrier cards. It will be recycled after the current Border Chronicle project is completed.

data.name: Black Ore Fragments
data.introduction: The ferrous metal ores have evolved into a new type of mineral under the influence of Collapse radiation. It is no longer possible to extract ferrous metals as in the past. They have lost their activity and have become very stable. They can be combined with glass-like crystals in the analysis machine to produce directional carrier cards. They will be recovered after the current Boundary Chronicle Project is completed.

data.name: Copolymer Core
data.introduction: It's probably a mechanical product from the early years. Under the influence of the Collapse Storm, the metal parts were covered with multiple layers of hard copolymer shells, and the interior was also eroded by the Collapse Particles, making it impossible to trace its previous function and form. It can be combined with glass-like crystals in the analysis machine to make a location-oriented carrier card. It will be collected after the current Boundary Chronicle Project is completed.

data.name: Exotic Alloy
data.introduction: Formed mainly by amorphous metals affected by collapse radiation, with a higher melting point, they can still quickly transform between solid and liquid. They can be combined with glass-like crystals in the analysis machine to make position-oriented carrier cards. They will be recovered after the current Boundary Chronicle project is completed.

data.name: Iridescent Crystal Cluster
data.introduction: The crystal clusters with apparent play-of-color effects are of unknown origin. Some researchers have inferred from their structure that these crystal clusters result from abnormal changes during the formation of Collapse Crystals and do not store Collapse Particles themselves. However, in a radiation environment, their properties are very stable. They can be combined with glass-like crystals in the analysis machine to make position-oriented carrier cards. They will be recovered after the completion of the current Boundary Chronicle Project.

data.name: Color-Shift Rock
data.introduction: Originally, the stone was covered with a large number of moss plants. After the atomic explosion, Collapse radiation spread over a large area, causing the plants to die, but the decayed substances produced by the death of some plants accidentally penetrated into the rock and were preserved. This effect is similar to dyeing, so it is named 'Color Shift'. It can be combined with glass-like crystals in the analysis machine to make functional directional carrier cards. These will be recovered after the current Border Chronicle project is completed.

data.name: Silicon Carbide Composite
data.introduction: After years of impact from Collapse particles and scraping from collapse storms, a silicon carbide composite was formed, which can only be seen in legends. It is one of the materials used to make carrier cards that acquire specific "specific functional type" signals.

data.name: Polyethylene Crystallization
data.introduction: After years of impact from Collapse particles and the scraping of collapse storms, a type of frosted glass that can only be seen in legends has been formed. It is one of the materials used to make carrier cards that obtain specific "specific functional type" signals.

data.name: Dark Tinted Glass Tower
data.introduction: Initially, it was various artificial glass fragments. After the survey area was abandoned, these glass fragments were affected by years of collapse particles and scraped by collapse storms. They eventually formed into dark sand glass towers that should not appear in this world and were called god-level. It has a tiny bonus for making carrier cards that obtain specific 'perfect weapon attachment' signals and is also one of the materials.

data.name: Glass Tower of Glazed Sand
data.introduction: Initially, it was a variety of gravitational polymers. After the survey area was abandoned, these glass fragments were influenced by years of collapse particles and scraped by collapse storms, eventually forming a god-level glazed sand glass tower that should not appear in this world. It has a significant bonus for making carrier cards that obtain specific 'perfect weapon attachment' signals and is also one of the materials.

data.name: Radiant Colored Sand Glass Tower
data.introduction: Initially, it was various dark matter crystals. After the survey area was abandoned, these glass fragments were influenced by Collapse particles over the years and worn down by Collapse storms. Eventually, they formed into a god-level shining sand glass tower that shouldn't exist in this world. It provides a massive bonus for making carrier cards that obtain specific 'perfect weapon attachment' signals and is also one of the materials.

data.introduction:

A gift voucher issued to celebrate this anniversary. With this in hand, one can exchange for their desired gifts!
Can be used at the Gift Exchange to redeem rewards.

To prepare newbies for an entry assessment, the logistics staff have prepares sufficient supplies.
Can be used to exchange rewards in Logistics Support.

data.name: Assessment Points

data.name: Exclusive Cake 2024
data.introduction:
A gift to the Commander from everyone aboard the Elmo, to celebrate this special day.

"Regardless of whether our future is stormy or clear, we'll always be by your side, Commander!"

data.name: Exquisite Gift Box
data.introduction:
A pile of assorted gifts and cards have appeared overnight at the door to the Commander's Dorm.

"I wonder whose gift the Commander will like the most..."
You remember someone whispering such in the midst of your dreams last night.

data.name: Exclusive Cake 2025
data.introduction:
A gift to the Commander from everyone aboard the Elmo, to celebrate this special day.

"May all your aspirations be realized, all your dreams come true, and your journey be filled with happiness, laughter... and us."

data.name: New Year's Eve Photo
data.introduction:
Lights, camera, the Commander's throne... All set.

"Be sure to maintain your smile through the moment the fireworks bloom, Commander! This is our first group photo for the new year!"

data.name: New Year Firework 108
data.introduction:
Homemade fireworks created by eager members of the Elmo. Without realizing it, the festive atmosphere has already spread throughout the vehicle.

"Happy new year, Commander. If you're bothered by the noise, I can help you cup our ears."

data.name: Sweet Affection
data.introduction:
This is perhaps one of the busiest days in the Elmo's kitchen. The air is filed with the scent of sweets, as moving as a girl's feelings.

"Commander, each and every one of our creations of love are one of a kind."

data.name: Fine Wine Under the Moon
data.introduction:
"Mayling endured the pain and contributed this Treasured Wine. The moonlight poured into the cups, and the mellow aroma of the wine has attracted lovers of it.

"Commander, to reunions and celebrations— Cheers!"

data.name: Gingerbread Tin
data.introduction:
A huge tin of gingerbread cookies that appeared on the Commander's table upon waking up one morning. Each gingerbread cookie is illustrated with a different design. Analysis of the artstyle indicates that most members on the Elmo were involved.

"Let's keep quiet and be careful not to wake up the Commander, we'll draw them one by one..."
You faintly remember hearing people whispering with care in the midst of your dreams last night.

data.name: Mementos of Time
data.introduction: “Our journey will not end here like this. Someday in the future, we will meet again and continue travelling together.”

data.name: Exquisite Curio - Deichgraf
data.introduction:
“All those airdropped armor packs were hard to handle... I should have Mayling look into replicating a similar system for the Elmo.”
It's big and very detailed... Looks like somebody had very vivid recollections of it.

data.name: Exquisite Curio - Ledyanaya Mogila
data.introduction:
“It looks pretty cool. If it had more firepower, fighting it would be more worthwhile.”
It's big and very detailed... Looks like somebody had very vivid recollections of it.

data.name: Exquisite Curio - Thoad
data.introduction:
“If only it could attract fortune...”
It's big and very detailed... Looks like somebody had very vivid recollections of it.

data.name: Exquisite Curio - Terrorhorn Chimera
data.introduction:
“What the heck, it looks kind of cute in model form...”
It's big and very detailed... Looks like somebody had very vivid recollections of it.

data.name: Exquisite Curio - Thorn
data.introduction:
“It's fluffy, but it looks super vicious and it's not cute at all.”
It's big and very detailed... Looks like somebody had very vivid recollections of it.

data.name: Strange Curio - Super Dinergate
data.introduction: “It's hard to look it directly in its big red eye. Feels like there's someone behind it, gazing at me...”

data.name: Strange Curio - Aegis Bulwark
data.introduction: “Who doesn't love giant robots? It's only now that I've discovered the rugged, solid charm of this model.”

data.name: Strange Curio - FRZ Thoad
data.introduction: I understand the principle behind it, but why doesn't it hibernate in winter?

data.name: Strange Curio - COR Thoad
data.introduction: Is it really safe to put it here? It looks to be as toxic as ever...

data.name: Strange Curio - HYD Thoad
data.introduction: “It's sticky and slimy and I never want to touch another toad again.”

data.name: Strange Curio - Thorn
data.introduction: “It's fluffy, but it looks super vicious and it's not cute at all.”

data.name: Strange Curio - Deichgraf
data.introduction: “All those airdropped armor packs were hard to handle... I should have Mayling look into replicating a similar system for the Elmo.”

data.name: Strange Curio - Ledyanaya Mogila
data.introduction: “It looks pretty cool. If it had more firepower, fighting it would be more worthwhile.”

data.name: Strange Curio - Tumorhynchus
data.introduction: It reminds me of a dragonfruit for some reason... I hope nobody on the Elmo gets it into their head to try and use it for cooking.

data.name: Strange Curio - Blusphere
data.introduction: “Dona eius requiem.”

data.name: Strange Curio - Terrorhorn Chimera
data.introduction: “What the heck, it looks kind of cute in model form...”

data.name: Strange Curio - Creepy Doll
data.introduction: “If only she could have joined the Elmo's Doll complement...”

data.name: Curio Color Scheme - Grid
data.introduction:
A classic coloration that projects an air of solemnity. 
Can be used to change the material of the Curio Display cabinet.

data.name: Curio Color Scheme - Woodgrain
data.introduction:
Its rich wood texture is the perfect frame for your memories. 
Can be used to change the material of the Curio Display cabinet.

data.name: Curio Color Scheme - Spotless
data.introduction:
This chiaroscuro brings freshness to the past. 
Can be used to change the material of the Curio Display cabinet.

data.name: Curio Display Cabinet - Type 1

data.name: Curio Selection - Fireline
data.introduction:
A trove of many mixed memories. Which one has left the deepest impression on you?
After opening, you will randomly receive one of the following Curios, with a chance of obtaining an Exquisite Curio: Strange Curio - Deichgraf, Strange Curio - Ledyanaya Mogila, Strange Curio - Tumorhynchus, Strange Curio - Blusphere, Strange Curio - Terrorhorn Chimera, Strange Curio - Creepy Doll.

data.name: Breath of the Cool
data.introduction: This simple, clean and plain ensemble nevertheless manages to perfectly showcase Vector's charm.

data.name: Marvelous Teddy
data.introduction: Headwear themed after a bearcub. Its new and intriguing style makes people want to stroke it.

data.name: Naughty Kitten
data.introduction: A cat-ear headband from days past. Who would have thought that it originated in a mission that Vector never wanted to take on?

data.name: Abounding Youth
data.introduction: Themed after an Occidental school uniform, this outfit abounds with the vigor and passion of youth. This is quite a stylish experience for Vector.

data.name: Nostalgia Style
data.introduction: Based on the Vector SMG combined with a simple white top, it emphasises the wearer's cool elegance. Putting it on makes you feel like you're back in the old days.

data.name: Kitty Paws
data.introduction: A revamped version of an outfit she once wore on a dorky mission. Since the chance to do so doesn't come by often, why not make a "kitty's-got-claws" gesture while going "nani nani" once again?

data.name: Schoolyard Cruise
data.introduction: Youth, life, cheeriness and vitality - is school the only place where you can experience these things?

data.name: Tactical Style
data.introduction: Stockings made for combat, preaching the gospel of utilitarianism.

data.name: Nimble Kitty
data.introduction: A design that combines fashionable asymmetry and the glory of cats. It doesn't boost jumping power, but cute is justice.

data.name: Unmarred Edge
data.introduction: Unburdened by extraneous ornamentation, just like Klukai's fighting style. As the strands of her hair ripple in the wind, you can almost hear the roar of engines.

data.name: Lightspeed Lens
data.introduction: These sunglasses perched on her head are both a practical accessory for a rider and a fashion statement for her racing form.

data.name: Turbokat Resonance
data.introduction: Her earphones pulse with music, as though they've found the resonant frequency of the wind and her engines. The cat-eared design reveals the cute side of her stylish self.

data.name: Roaming Core
data.introduction: Her rider's outfit is tailored to fit the needs of her racing style, turning her into a glint of speeding light as she streaks through the night.

data.name: Superspeed Liberation
data.introduction: Having discarded all unnecessary tactical components, this lightweight rider's outfit sticks to her frame like a second skin.

data.name: Star-Studded Sidereal Course
data.introduction: This outfit preserves as much storage space as possible while eliminating excess weight, the better to handle unexpected circumstances on her journey.

data.name: Abyssal Wayfarer
data.introduction: These black hotpants emphasise her frame's curves, and the tactical pockeys are loaded with spare magazines and tools. These are the unique, practical aesthetics of a lone wanderer.

data.name: Phantom Raid
